BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF OHIO:
Section 1. That section 2917.43 of the Revised Code be 6
enacted to read as follows: 7
Sec. 2917.43. (A) As used in this section : 8
(1) "Cloud seeding" means a form of weather modification 9
where a pollutant is released into clouds to induce or enhance 10
precipitation. 11
(2) "Marine cloud brightening" means enhancing the 12
reflectivity of low-lying marine clouds to reflect more 13
sunlight. 14
(3) "Pollutant" means any aerosol; biologic, 15
transbiologic, or genetically modified agent; chaff; metal; 16
radioactive material; acid; alkali; chemical; particulate; 17
contaminant; smart dust; smoke; soot; fume; vapor; air pollutant 18

